Well Here's the profile for my monk:<br>
<br>
Name: Unknown, just call him monky<br>
Blood Type: O <br>
Born: South India?<br>
Powers: Can summon gods to do his bidding<br>
Likes to: Laugh and Stay fit<br>
Hates: Foolish people<br>
Weapon: Long mystic bamboo sword in which he summons gods with<br>
<br>
PROFILE:<br>
This monk has been a very social butterfly throughout the ages. Ages meaning a long time back, you see this monk, was born exactly 100 years ago. Which technically makes him pretty ancient to a normal human. Trapped in a prison, showcased to people, to show them the wonders of age. It never worked. But that was how he could put food on the table. But one day, while walking thru the woods he found a beautiful bamboo sword, lying ontop of a rock between the pond. Out of curiosity he jumped to the rock and picked up the sword. Suddenly, there was a flash of light and he became one with it. Harnessing all energy the user of this device he waits to prove his power. But this sword was not just any sword. It was a heavenly sword touched by ancient gods of his land. <br>
He now has the ability to shout towards the sky and down comes help. But now, he travels throughout the world in search of worthy opponents, fighting demons, dragons, ogre like whales and anthros with basilisks, and everything else imaginable. He comes to the Great Magician's Gala. This shall be his last stop to gain all imformation thru challenges with wizards, sorceresses and other magic users from all over. <br>
